benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/admin/healthcheck - Put the host back into rotation

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios cover successful PUT requests with expected status codes and outcomes.
Authorization: Scenarios test unauthorized access and insufficient permissions with appropriate error codes.
Concurrency Issues: Scenarios test multiple concurrent requests and ensure no race conditions.
Server Error Handling: Scenarios cover service unavailability and network interruptions.
gaps: Partial Update: No scenarios explicitly test rejection of partial updates.
Non-Existing Resource: No scenarios test handling of PUT requests to non-existing resources.
Rate Limiting: No tests cover how the system handles multiple requests in a short time.
recommendations: Add tests to ensure partial updates are rejected unless allowed.
Include scenarios for handling PUT requests to non-existing resources.
Add rate limiting tests to ensure the system handles multiple requests in a short time appropriately.
